/* Advent of Code 2015 Day 1: Not Quite Lisp.
1: Find the number you get from counting up and down with two symbols.
2: Find the first time that number becomes negative.
If all is successful, using included input, the output should be 232 for 1 and 1783 for 2.
Functional when compiled with tdm-gcc using the C/C++ Compile Run extension for Visual Studio Code as of March 19, 2024.
*/
